narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: How to write good bullets! And how to engage in meaningful military current events conversation.
Practical information regarding serving as in officer in the USAF.
Knowledge of topics relevant to Air Force Officers
Learned practical information and tips about Air Force careers. The best part was hearing personal and anecdotes and advice from Maj Moen.
I learned Air Force appropriate cost-benefit analysis, risk management, personnel management, and writing skills.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments:
Strengths: a really good learning environment 
Weakness: too long of a time block. We didnt have material to fill it
Lots of potentially boring topics, but most class discussions were productive and engaging.
Enjoyed the discussions on current events topics and really think that is a useful addition to the base curriculum

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would only recommend to AFROTC cadets.
Yes if you are in ROTC
